      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor \u2013 absolutely pristine inside and out! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that brand-new feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been kept in truly perfect shape, this is the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
