    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response. Mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, the drivetrain is mechanically flawless. Critically, the rod bearings have been replaced, the VANOS system overhauled, and the rear subframe reinforced\u2014addressing all platform-specific weak points. The chassis retains its original factory rigidity with no oxidation, riding on a perfectly tuned MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension. The exterior finish is concours-level, free of imperfections, and the interior remains in showroom state. A turn-key masterpiece for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
