    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true collector-grade specimen, maintained with an obsessive attention to detail that is immediately apparent. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish with zero road rash or swirling, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin still carries that signature 'new car' scent; the premium leather seats show absolutely no bolster wear, and every switch operates with a crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach\u2014always garage-kept, never driven in inclement weather, and accompanied by a meticulous folder of every service record since day one. This isn't just a used vehicle; it\u2019s a time capsule. I welcome any pre-purchase inspection to verify that this car meets the highest standards of excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
